This project uses shadcn-phlex — all shadcn/ui components ported to Phlex for Rails.

RULES:
- Use ui_* Kit helpers for all UI: ui_button, ui_card, ui_dialog, ui_text_field, etc.
- Never use raw HTML for components that exist (buttons, badges, cards, alerts, separators, skeletons)
- Semantic colors: bg-primary, text-muted-foreground — never bg-blue-500 or text-gray-600
- No space-y-* / space-x-*. Use flex flex-col gap-* or flex gap-*
- Form controls need name: for submission: ui_checkbox(name: "user[terms]")
- Use ui_text_field for labeled inputs, not manual Field + Label + Input
- Stimulus controllers are auto-wired. Never manually add data-controller
- Dialog/Sheet/Drawer always need a Title component for accessibility
- Items go inside their parent: SelectItem inside SelectContent, CommandItem inside CommandGroup

FORM FIELDS:
  ui_text_field(label: "Email", name: "user[email]", type: "email", error: @errors[:email]&.first)
  ui_checkbox(name: "user[terms]", checked: true)
  ui_switch(name: "user[notify]", checked: false)
  ui_select(name: "user[role]") { ui_select_trigger { ui_select_value(placeholder: "Role") }; ui_select_content { ui_select_item(value: "admin") { "Admin" } } }

COMMON PATTERNS:
  ui_button(variant: :destructive, size: :sm) { "Delete" }
  ui_card { ui_card_header { ui_card_title { "T" } }; ui_card_content { "..." } }
  ui_dialog { ui_dialog_trigger { "Open" }; ui_dialog_content { ui_dialog_header { ui_dialog_title { "T" } } } }
  ui_tabs(value: "a") { ui_tabs_list { ui_tabs_trigger(value: "a") { "A" } }; ui_tabs_content(value: "a") { "..." } }
  ui_table { ui_table_header { ui_table_row { ui_table_head { "Col" } } }; ui_table_body { ui_table_row { ui_table_cell { "Val" } } } }
